## iommus

**Value type:** `<prop-encoded-array>` encoded as a list of phandle + iommu-specifier pairs

A list of phandle and IOMMU specifier pairs specifying the IOMMU master interfaces of the device. Each pair identifies an IOMMU controller and the stream ID (or equivalent specifier) used by the device on that IOMMU.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
usb_1: usb@a6f8800 {
    compatible = "qcom,sm8550-dwc3";
    iommus = <&apps_smmu 0xe0 0x0>;
};
```
